sequenceDiagram
    participant O as Orchestrator
    participant W1 as Worktree 1<br>modularization
    participant W2 as Worktree 2<br>reduce_any_types
    participant W3 as Worktree 3<br>test_suite
    participant WN as Worktree N<br>task_N
    participant QA as QA Pipeline
    participant MQ as Merge Queue

    Note over O: Specs ready: 91 tasks

    O->>W1: git worktree add + spawn agent
    O->>W2: git worktree add + spawn agent
    O->>W3: git worktree add + spawn agent
    O->>WN: git worktree add + spawn agent

    par Parallel Execution (all isolated)
        activate W1
        W1->>W1: Read spec, implement changes
        W1->>W1: Commit to auto/modularization
        Note over W1: 62 sessions
        deactivate W1

        activate W2
        W2->>W2: Read spec, implement changes
        W2->>W2: Commit to auto/reduce_any_types
        Note over W2: 60 sessions
        deactivate W2

        activate W3
        W3->>W3: Read spec, implement changes
        W3->>W3: Commit to auto/test_suite
        Note over W3: 57 sessions
        deactivate W3

        activate WN
        WN->>WN: Read spec, implement changes
        WN->>WN: Commit to auto/task_N
        Note over WN: N sessions
        deactivate WN
    end

    W1->>QA: Submit completed work
    W2->>QA: Submit completed work
    W3->>QA: Submit completed work
    WN->>QA: Submit completed work

    activate QA
    Note over QA: 71 QA reports generated

    QA-->>W2: Rejected: fix bcrypt + lastUsedAt
    activate W2
    W2->>W2: Apply fixes in isolated worktree
    W2->>QA: Resubmit
    deactivate W2
    Note over QA: ~95% pass on 2nd attempt

    QA->>MQ: Approved tasks
    deactivate QA

    activate MQ
    Note over MQ: Priority-weighted merge order
    MQ->>MQ: Foundation tasks first
    MQ->>MQ: Conflict detection
    MQ->>MQ: Merge to main
    Note over MQ: 90 branches integrated
    deactivate MQ
